IFM - Lightweight Ncurses File Manager
======================================
Controls:
  [K/J]        Move up/down
  [Enter/L]    Open file/dir
  [H]          Go back
  [CTRL + H]   Toggle hidden files
  [Alt + H]    Go home
  [T]          Create file
  [M]          Create dir
  [Delete]     Delete file/dir
  [R]          Rename file/dir
  [SHIFT+O]    Open with custom viewer
  [Q]          Exit
  [F1]         Help
  [F2]         Open menu (LICENSE, COMMANDS, ABOUT)
  [:]          Enter command mode
  [gg]         Go to the first file
  [G]          Go to the last file

Command Mode:
  [cd <dir>]   Change directory
  [h]          Show hidden files
  [uh]         Hide hidden files
  [q]          Quit
  [G]          Go to the first file
  [g]          Go to the last file


Mouse Controls:
  [Left Click]  Select/Open file/dir
  [Right Click] Go back
  [Scroll Up]   Move up
  [Scroll Down] Move down
